The paper discusses the development of a deep neural network for pattern classification, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of ridge regression and kernelization also suggests a focus on numerical optimization (cs.NE) and statistical learning (cs.SD).
